+# Verification Report — T-018@20260425T183959Zd
+
+**Verify Agent:** Codex
+**Date:** 2026-04-26
+**Artifacts Reviewed:**
+- [my-claw/tools/senseweave/phrase_capture.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/my-claw/tools/senseweave/phrase_capture.py)
+- [my-claw/tools/senseweave/phrase_capture_runtime.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/my-claw/tools/senseweave/phrase_capture_runtime.py)
+- [my-claw/tools/midi_keyboard_listener.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/my-claw/tools/midi_keyboard_listener.py)
+- [my-claw/tools/theramini_listener.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/my-claw/tools/theramini_listener.py)
+- [my-claw/tools/human_phrase_capture_verify.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/my-claw/tools/human_phrase_capture_verify.py)
+- [tests/test_phrase_capture_runtime.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/tests/test_phrase_capture_runtime.py)
+- [tests/test_midi_keyboard_listener_runtime.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/tests/test_midi_keyboard_listener_runtime.py)
+- [tests/test_theramini_listener_runtime.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/tests/test_theramini_listener_runtime.py)
+- [tests/test_human_phrase_capture_verify.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/tests/test_human_phrase_capture_verify.py)
+- [specs/t-018@20260425t183959zd-spec.md](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/specs/t-018@20260425t183959zd-spec.md)
+- [ESCALATIONS.md](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/ESCALATIONS.md)
+
+## Correctness
+The remaining verifier gap from T-018@20260425T183959Zc is closed. `ActiveSongPhraseCapture` now derives song-scoped sidecar metadata from `/tmp/composer_state.json`, resets partial phrases when the song context disappears or changes, and feeds the existing `PhraseCaptureWriter` only during active songs. `midi_keyboard_listener.py` now forwards live MIDI bytes into `samples/keyboard/`, and `theramini_listener.py` now forwards the post-idle-tone play decision plus decoded audio chunks into `samples/theramini/`.
+
+## Completeness
+Both human-input sources are covered end to end:
+- keyboard active-song phrase simulation writes a `.mid` plus a valid sidecar
+- Theramini active-song phrase simulation writes a `.wav` plus a valid sidecar
+- inactive/song-less composer state writes nothing and drops buffered partial phrases
+- the hardware-free verifier script exercises both paths together and reports the captured paths plus JSON metadata
+
+## Consistency
+The change follows the existing sampler verification pattern already used by `sample_capture_verify.py`, `composer_quote_verify.py`, and `self_listener_quote_verify.py`: add a deterministic repo-backed verifier script, then pin it with tests. Listener integration stays additive by wrapping the already-landed `PhraseCaptureWriter` instead of replacing the listener state model or adding a second capture authority.
+
+## Security
+No new dependency or filesystem-scope risk was introduced. Capture paths still resolve under the configured sample root, sidecars still go through the locked schema validator, and the new runtime wrapper reads only the existing composer authority file.
+
+## Quality
+The regression surface is strong:
+- `pytest tests/test_phrase_capture.py tests/test_phrase_capture_runtime.py tests/test_midi_keyboard_listener_runtime.py tests/test_theramini_listener_runtime.py tests/test_human_phrase_capture_verify.py -q`
+- `python my-claw/tools/human_phrase_capture_verify.py --capture-root /tmp/promptclaw-t018-verify`
+- `pip install -e '.[dev]' && pytest tests/ -x && ruff check src/ tests/ && mypy src/`
+
+Manual verifier output confirmed the expected directories and tags:
+- `keyboard_path=/tmp/promptclaw-t018-verify/keyboard/keyboard_19700101T000146Z_77f41ce6.mid`
+- `theramini_path=/tmp/promptclaw-t018-verify/theramini/theramini_19700101T000146Z_fe6421a3.wav`
+- `keyboard_metadata={"duration": 6.0, "instrument": "midi_keyboard", "key": "Dm", "song_id": "verify-song-1", "source": "human", "tempo": 96, "timestamp": "1970-01-01T00:01:46Z"}`
+- `theramini_metadata={"duration": 6.0, "instrument": "theramini", "key": "Dm", "song_id": "verify-song-1", "source": "human", "tempo": 96, "timestamp": "1970-01-01T00:01:46Z"}`
+- `HUMAN_PHRASE_CAPTURE_OK`
+
